00:00:06.900 --> 00:00:09.300
Chocolate Fondant Cake

00:00:09.300 --> 00:00:11.600
Serves: 8

00:00:11.600 --> 00:00:16.300
Equipment: 23 cm diameter cake mould

00:00:16.300 --> 00:00:17.600
Ingredients

00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:22.700
125 g dark chocolate, broken into pieces

00:00:22.700 --> 00:00:28.300
125 g butter, cut into small cubes

00:00:28.300 --> 00:00:33.300
125 g (½ cup + 2 tbsp) sugar

00:00:33.300 --> 00:00:36.500
60 g (½ cup) flour, sifted 

00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:41.600
3 eggs, yolks and whites separated

00:00:41.600 --> 00:00:42.900
Directions

00:00:42.900 --> 00:00:51.600
Melt the chocolate and butter over a bain-marie

00:00:51.600 --> 00:00:57.800
Remove the bowl from the heat and add the sugar and mix well

00:00:57.800 --> 00:01:11.500
Add egg yolks, one by one then stir in the flour

00:01:11.500 --> 00:01:32.300
Whisk the egg whites to firm peak and gradually fold into the chocolate batter

00:01:32.300 --> 00:01:35.500
Pour the batter into the mould lined with a disk of parchment paper

00:01:35.500 --> 00:01:46.000
and bake in the preheated oven to 165°C for 20 - 25 minutes

